headline.main: Gift Food Packages Reach Britain Safely; Only One Small Ship Out of 15 Sunk So Far

lead_paragraph: Fourteen out of fifteen ships carrying packages of rationed food-stuffs to Great Britain have been safely convoyed across the Atlantic from New York, officials of the British-American Trading Corporation disclosed yesterday.
